[Most countries in Europe are experiencing exponential 'second' waves with a variety of restriction measures being put in place to control the spread of the virus. Until such time that a vaccine is available and administered, the stop-gap measures such as lockdown, enforcing distancing etc will have to remain in place , albeit at un-precedented economic and human costs- some ways to go yet... it worked during the early waves and can help stop virus transmission. - Mod.UBA]

